org.activebpel.rt.bpeladmin.war.web.processview
Class AeProcessViewBean

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.bpeladmin.war.web.processview.AeProcessViewBase
      org.activebpel.rt.bpeladmin.war.web.processview.AeProcessViewBean
public class AeProcessViewBean
extends AeProcessViewBase

This bean is responsible for providing BPEL activity attribute data as well as other details (when applicable) such as variable state information.

Method Detail

retrieveProperties

protected void retrieveProperties()
Retrieves the BPEL element's attribute (such as name), as well as additional data such a instance variable information.

This method is invoked when the path to the element is set. Assumes that the active process id has already been set via SetProcessId() method i.e. call SetProcessId(pid) first, followed by SetPath(theLocationPath).
